thread.title: Donald Trump Descends on Skeptical Davos Audience

author: Rebecca Ballhaus
title: Donald Trump Descends on Skeptical Davos Audience
text:
DAVOS, Switzerland—President Donald Trump’s arrival at the World Economic Forum here on Thursday was met with an immediate question: “Are you going to be treated well?”
Mr. Trump, whose debut inside the hall hushed the crowded space except for the snapping of cellphone photos, replied: “You tell me.”
